node.text: @tsarasmith not heard of that! I’ll have a look 🙌

The last couple of years I’ve really been enjoying exploring more and more of Dartmoor national park! 

Although on this particular day, the weather wasn’t the best, it was still great fun scrambling up Haytor!.. keeps swiping for a bit of reality😂😂

Where is your favourite spot on Dartmoor?

#dartmoornationalpark #dartmoor #haytor #hikinguk #scrambling #ukhikes #ukhiking #adventureseeker
@lil.explores I diddd! It was fab thankyou 😍
Amazing ! Hope you had the best adventure ❤️
Haha 😅 I know that section well ! 😁 I spent a good 15 min looking at how to climb that section without dying 🤣
@jack_hellyar I’ll have to check that out 😍
@tsarasmith not heard of that! I’ll have a look 🙌
I love Grimspound. Something special there.
Haytor is lovely! The spot around Lydford is quite lovely too. But as you say, there's so much in Dartmoor to explore, it's on my list for sure 👍
